hopobject.body: Do you play any instruments? buy tretinoin uk Shania Twain's New Year's Day 2011 wedding to Frederic Thiebaud was a picture-perfect affair to remember. The country superstar donned a beautiful strapless dress as she and the Swiss businessman tied the knot during a romantic oceanside ceremony in Puerto Rico. Her gown, purchased from a small boutique in Switzerland, was paired with Lorraine Schwartz jewelry and Calvin Klein shoes. Celebrity photographer Robert Evans captured the couple's big day, which was shared with 40 of their closest family and friends. Twain's 9-year-old son, Eja, walked her down the aisle.
